        "text": "[[Work Splits]] offer a mechanism to keep to a schedule that can be initiated from within a development group. If a Product Initiative is in jeprody because [[Implied Requirements]] cannot be met through schedule and [[Work Queue]] adjustments, then it is unlikely any other development initiated activity will help. "
